$interpreted: Dagger: ARGH! I've spent enough time following tracks. Where have the humans taken Angelia to?
Dagger: I'm in this for the long haul! Can't run forever!
Roger: ...An abandoned rune chariot, but why?
Roger: A Bear?! On Paradise Prairie?
Dagger: Didn't think I'd make it this far in life, huh? Spit it out, where is Angelia?
Roger: Angelia? Princess of the Kingdom of the Sun?
Dagger: Quit playing dumb. You're standing next to the kidnapper's rune chariot, drop the act.
Roger: Wait, let me explain. I didn't kidnap the princess——
Dagger: This is unbearable, I don't want to hear anything from you! I'll take the words right out of your mouth!
Roger: HEY, you big fat teddy bear! Care to hear me out!?
Dagger: Giving up already? Too late for that!
